bnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhPKhSj.png&h=a2cc743d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成程望下山望下海咁，個人鍾意行島多過山，因為行山會好易悶，但真係幾多人下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋揀向右行<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGsDnkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGsDnkg.jpg&h=9e0f895c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同朋友嚟一個螳螂捕蟬，黃雀在後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時鳩下鳩下都幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9yK2kX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9yK2kX.jpg&h=12af42c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話條條大路通羅馬，你話~記得搽防曬同蚊怕水，樓豬俾啲腳膠蚊奶到紅哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKdnO1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKdnO1v.jpg&h=11c917da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOR42mt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOR42mt.jpg&h=84ef1492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vj0UE8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVj0UE8b.jpg&h=dcafc601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行落去長樓梯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5prkAHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5prkAHg.jpg&h=b5a788b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺朵花好似每個男人中學都會經歷過嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2wwHn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2wwHn6.jpg&h=81f25907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知做乜會有張枱喺度，係咪CityU張枱飛咗過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DMdbgA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DMdbgA.jpg&h=3d78e910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度有個石刻文物，完成儀式就可以入錫克教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sLp2oP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sLp2oP.jpg&h=88e7a712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主亦不忘自拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOPino8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOPino8.jpg&h=1db4b0a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Pzm4CP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Pzm4CP.jpg&h=893cd047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDPBTwa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDPBTwa.jpg&h=d049740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個fd肚餓得濟要返轉頭食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該每個島嘅餐蛋麵都俾我食過哂，28大洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM8Gkbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM8Gkbh.jpg&h=12ab0574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完向返左行去燈塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解見唔到yylam<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmkdVK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmkdVK2.jpg&h=350d8d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnWQdw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnWQdw9.jpg&h=f154c322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n驚見Thanos個下巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yU9RHqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyU9RHqA.jpg&h=23f2467e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨走前走執咗袋垃圾，個沙灘乾淨過東平洲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMybHra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMybHra.jpg&h=7636162e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個仆街漏咗對西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9ofpEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9ofpEG.jpg&h=61ccb73e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後五點八搭船返歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rXs70dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrXs70dc.jpg&h=68abdf7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"樓主一定好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da6c98806b08fe58b7b2aad1985f333558c2756","tid":2193040,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a83fa7777d9ac1db0096f1df719d3ed0878ad88","tid":2193040,"uid":172295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"馬丁巴收唔收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"唔收，女朋友就要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02632fe6f6a83534a484112ba32087efc4103072","tid":2193040,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c3c3217ba177e1732df6cb